{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/SlothySample","doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"title":"Essentials"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}],"title":"Getting Started with Sloths","role":"article","images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"gettingStarted-card.png"}]},"kind":"article","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths are complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every sloth has a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". You can optionally provide a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}]},{"text":"Create a Sloth","anchor":"Create-a-Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fire"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"wind","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lightning"},{"type":"text","text":", you can specify this at creation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat","text":"Provide a Habitat","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel","isActive":true},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Exercise a Sloth","anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol and implementing the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth","text":"Feed a Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food"},{"type":"text","text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:"}]},{"code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth","type":"heading","text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a "},{"code":"Date","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and an ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"references":{"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Sloth/energyLevel":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy level of the sloth."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","title":"energyLevel","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/sloth\/energylevel","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energyLevel"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}]},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator":{"title":"SlothCreator","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Catalog sloths you find in nature and create new adorable virtual sloths."}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator","role":"collection","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"slothCreator-icon.png"}],"kind":"symbol"},"slothPower.png":{"identifier":"slothPower.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/slothPower@2x.png","traits":["2x","light"]},{"traits":["2x","dark"],"url":"\/images\/slothPower~dark@2x.png"}],"type":"image","alt":"A diagram with the five sloth power types: ice, fire, wind, lightning, and none."},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Activity/perform(with:)":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Performs the work or sequence of actions for an activity."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","title":"perform(with:)","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/activity\/perform(with:)","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"perform"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"with"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Sloth","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SlothCreator0A0V"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Speed","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SlothCreator5SpeedO"}],"required":true},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Habitat/comfortLevel":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An indicator of how comfortable a sloth might find the habitat."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/habitat\/comfortlevel","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword